<ulink url="http://www.linux-ha.org">Projet Linux-HA (Libre)</ulink> &et; <ulink url="http://www.uow.edu.au/~andrewm/linux/ext3/">ext3</ulink>
</para>
</listitem>
</ItemizedList>
</para> 
